OL,7,FA pioneering procedure that could
OL,8,Ftransform the lives of thousands of
OL,9,Fpeople who suffer from heart
OL,10,Firregularities has been carried out in
OL,11,FHampshire.
OL,13,FDoctors at University Hospital
OL,14,FSouthampton have fitted a new type of
OL,15,Fpacemaker involving two separate
OL,16,Fdevices that can communicate with each
OL,17,Fother.
