OL,7,FThe system, which could be the
OL,8,Fsolution for patients whose bodies
OL,9,Fhave rejected single pacemakers, is
OL,10,Fthe first of its kind in the world.
OL,12,FKaren Cooper, who has had a pacemaker
OL,13,Fsince she was 17, has undergone the
OL,14,Fprocedure to have the new device
OL,15,Ffitted.
OL,17,FIt is made up of two capsules, which
OL,18,Fare placed in separate chambers of the
OL,19,Fheart.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
