OL,4,Cinvolving two separate devices carried
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FDr John Paisey, Consultant
OL,8,Fcardiologist said: "What's new now
OL,9,Fwith this device is we've got the
OL,10,Fextra sophistication of being able to
OL,11,Fstimulate both chambers of the heart -
OL,12,Fthe top chamber and the bottom chamber.
OL,14,F"We have those talk to each other, so
OL,15,Fthat the patient's heart beats in a
OL,16,Fmore physiological sequence. That's
OL,17,Fwhat we're so excited about with this
OL,18,Fdevice."
