OL,4,Cinvolving two separate devices carried
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FStandard pacemakers have a box
OL,8,Fimplanted under the skin but away from
OL,9,Fthe heart, with a wire or wires
OL,10,Frunning into it to deliver electrical
OL,11,Fpulses.
OL,13,FBut, for some patients, their bodies
OL,14,Fare unable to cope with the standard
OL,15,Fpacemakers.
OL,17,FKaren Cooper said: "Unfortunately, the
OL,18,Fpacemakers that I had on my shoulders,
OL,19,Fthey got infected. So, then I ended up
OL,20,Fwith a blood clot and I had to be put
OL,21,Fin the abdomen.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
