OL,3,CPioneering pacemaker procedure
OL,4,Cinvolving two separate devices carried
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"It's not stressful now and I can just
OL,8,Fget on with everything and I know that
OL,9,FI can't get any infections. It's got a
OL,10,Flonger battery life as well -
OL,11,Fbrilliant."
OL,13,FThe new pacemakers are more expensive,
OL,14,Fso for now, procedures will be limited
OL,15,Fto those most in need.
OL,17,F"The longer you have a pacemaker in
OL,18,Ffor, the greater the risk is of
OL,19,Fsomething going wrong with it at some
OL,20,Fstage in the future.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
