OL,4,Cinvolving two separate devices carried
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"So if we can move to a situation
OL,8,Fwhere more patients have this type of
OL,9,Fdevice upfront, we'll have less
OL,10,Fpatients having problems with life
OL,11,Fthreatening complications, such as
OL,12,Finfection requiring major surgery to
OL,13,Fremove the device."
OL,15,FThis could end up being a
OL,16,Frevolutionary approach that can
OL,17,Fimprove and save more peoples lives in
OL,18,Ffuture.
